msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Please. After you, Aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Huh!? What the hell? Cap?\r\nThis guy is<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "Shut yer trap!\r\nY'oughta be showin' some respect!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "This guy's my aniki now!\r\nAnd you fools'll call him aniki too!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "What!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "Aniki, this is the Hirose Family office.\r\nY'can use it however y'want."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "Hey Cap, is it true what Ino-san said\r\nabout Masuzoe gettin' the drop on you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Now ain't the time fer that, Yuta!\r\nGo n' grab us some drinks!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "Uh, right..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "Oh, that a light on?\r\nIs the patriarch here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "Yeah, he said he's free for a bit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "Now that's good timin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "Aniki, lemme introduce ya t'our\r\npatriarch. C'mon in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Hold on, Nagumo. You're not going to\r\nask me to swear an oath, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "I only came to say hi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "I know that.\r\nNow, go on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "What's goin' on? Yer embarrassin'\r\nus in front of our guest."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "Huh? You all good, Tagashira?\r\nYer nose's bleedin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "It's Matsunaga-aniki. There's a gang\r\nof dudes startin' a ruckus."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "We gotta go help 'im."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "Huh? What happened?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "These customers were talkin' shit on us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "Sayin' the food sucks, it's too expensive,\r\nthe women're ugly..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "And? Ain't that all true?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "Well yeah, but it got t'Matsunaga-aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "He punched one of 'em right in the face."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "What was he thinkin' doin' that!?\r\nY'can't just smack yer customers around."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "I can explain, Cap."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Earlier today, we got our asses\r\nhanded to us by Kiryu-san here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "Well, news of that's been spreading."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "Matsunaga-aniki couldn't just stand by while\r\nthey mocked the family, and he snapped."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "I ain't helpin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "Y'can't run a bar if yer gonna beat yer\r\ncustomers up over every little thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "This is on Matsunaga.\r\nLet 'em hit 'im."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "Y'can't be serious!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "He's goin' up against ten guys!\r\nThey're gonna kill him!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "Cap, we need to help Matsunaga-aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "I said, I ain't gonna go.\r\nOh, by the way, Tagashira..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "This guy's my new aniki, Kiryu-san.\r\nY'better treat him like family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "Then screw it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "We'll have'ta save 'im jus' the two of us!\r\nC'mon, Yuta!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "Coming!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "Sheesh. Sorry 'bout that, Aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "They don't got a lick of sense\r\nwhen it comes t'manners."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "You're gonna let them go?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "The younger guy had a knife on him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "Yeah, it's all good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "Y'remember Matsunaga, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "He was over with me n' Yuta\r\nwhen we were playin' baseball."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Right, I remember fighting three of you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "Well, Matsunaga's been runnin'\r\na bar called Moreno fer a while now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "He's always gettin' uppity at his customers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "This shit happens jus' about every day."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "Is this Moreno near here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "Huh? Yeah..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "It's 'cross the bar district,\r\njust a hair in front o' the arcade."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "By the way, Aniki...\r\nI'm the captain o' this family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "I'll keep everyone in line, y'hear?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "Oh, and think o' this place\r\nas yer home, Aniki. It ain't so bad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "If yer includin' me n' Hirose-san, there're\r\nonly five o' us in the whole family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "Y'can relax here whenever y'want."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "Aniki? Where're y'goin'?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "(So this is Moreno.\r\nMatsunaga should be in here...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "Wh-Who is this guy...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "Man, that's Kiryu-aniki fer ya!\r\nIncredible. Y'really showed 'em!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "You're a little late, Nagumo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "Well, I can't go 'round beatin' up\r\nour payin' customers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "Sorry fer not helpin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "Hey, Matsunaga.\r\nY'doin' okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "I was worried about ya, y'know?\r\nDon't that make ya happy?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "Anyway, Kiryu-aniki was real\r\nnice in drivin' those bastards off."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "Y'oughta be more grateful."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "K... Kiryu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "Yer that guy from the baseball game!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "Yep."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "Forget about all that, Matsunaga.\r\nKiryu here's my aniki now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "He's gonna be hanging 'round our\r\noffice now n' again, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "Y'best be givin' him the respect\r\nhe deserves, y'hear?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "What're y'sayin', Cap!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "Y'can't just let him in like this!\r\nAin't he s'posed to be our enemy?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "Shut it! Yesterday's enemy is today's aniki.\r\nGet yer head 'round that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "Or are ya sayin' y'can't follow orders?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "This ain't any ol' order!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "Jus' today, you picked a fight with\r\nthis guy. We backed ya up, too!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "Y'can't change yer mind that easy, Cap."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "How y'expect us to keep up!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "Ya selfish ingrate!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "Maybe consider who saved\r\nyer sorry ass jus' now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "If it weren't for Kiryu-aniki..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "...Who knows what kinda shape\r\nyou'd be in if he hadn't."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "Clear?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "This is my bar, y'know.\r\nY'can't talk to me like that here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "97||||4"
msgid "It ain't yours."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "I'm jus' lettin' you run it for me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "'Sides..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||||4"
msgid "...Weren't those customers\r\na buncha ship buildin' types?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||||4"
msgid "Y'know we can't raise our fists at 'em."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||||4"
msgid "They could bring us all down with a\r\nflick of the wrist if they wanted, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||||4"
msgid "Ya think y'could face Hirose-san\r\nif that happened?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "Um, Cap..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "Wait, Aniki!\r\nWhere're ya goin'?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "I haven't finished introducin' ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||||4"
msgid "I left my baby over at Kiyomi's bar."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||||4"
msgid "Sorry, but I've gotta get back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||||4"
msgid "Oh. In that case, can y'cruise on by\r\nour office tomorrow?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||||4"
msgid "I'll be waitin' by the door for ya,\r\nso come whenever's good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||||4"
msgid "Sure. I'll see you then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||||4"
msgid "Aniki! Thanks fer everythin'!\r\nStay safe on yer way home!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "114||||4"
msgid "This is kinda pathetic..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||||4"
msgid "For real..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116||||4"
msgid "(It's gotten late. I should go\r\npick up Haruto from Kiyomi's bar...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "117||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san! Are you okay?\r\nHow's Nagumo-kun?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "118||||4"
msgid "He's doing fine.\r\nSorry I was gone so long."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "119||||4"
msgid "Don't worry about it. I'm just\r\nglad you're back in one piece."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120||||4"
msgid "Sorry again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "121||||4"
msgid "So, what happened out there?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||||4"
msgid "Hold on, Kiryu-san.\r\nYou're joining the Hirose Family?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||||4"
msgid "What gave you that impression?\r\nThat's not it at all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||||4"
msgid "They just had me over as a guest.\r\nI'm not joining up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||||4"
msgid "Hm... Honestly, I'm not sure\r\nI see the difference."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||||4"
msgid "But you at least buried the hatchet\r\nwith Nagumo-kun, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128||||4"
msgid "That's good to hear."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "129||||4"
msgid "You know, he really saw you as\r\nhis enemy, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "130||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "131||||4"
msgid "Just so you know, I'm heading to\r\nthe Hirose office again tomorrow."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132||||4"
msgid "With everything that happened, I never\r\ngot to ask about Haruka or Haruto's dad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "133||||4"
msgid "Oh, so that's why you're\r\nspending time with them?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "134||||4"
msgid "This honestly isn't how\r\nI expected things to go..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "135||||4"
msgid "...But I guess that's life."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||||4"
msgid "Well, we should get going."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||||4"
msgid "Of course. Come back anytime."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||||4"
msgid "(I should head back to the apartment.\r\nIt's been a long night...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||||4"
msgid "(I'm exhausted.\r\nI should probably get to sleep.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||||4"
msgid "(Maybe I'll explore the town\r\na little longer first.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||||4"
msgid "(All right. Time for bed.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||||4"
msgid "(I should stop by the Hirose Family office.\r\nSomeone there might recognize Haruka.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||||4"
msgid "Aniki! An honor to have ya back!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "145||||4"
msgid "Good to see you again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "146||||4"
msgid "Yo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "147||||4"
msgid "Hey."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "148||||4"
msgid "Don't give yer guest that half-assed crap!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "149||||4"
msgid "I've been wonderin' something, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "150||||4"
msgid "What's the deal with that baby?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "151||||4"
msgid "I'll just say he's not my kid,\r\nand he's not my grandkid either."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "152||||4"
msgid "Sooo... Y'kidnapped him?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "153||||4"
msgid "'Course he didn't, ya numbnuts!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "154||||4"
msgid "What kinda guy d'ya think Aniki is!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "155||||4"
msgid "Uh, I can't actually deny that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156||||4"
msgid "Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "157||||4"
msgid "Anyway, this is Haruto.\r\nI'm looking for his father."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "158||||4"
msgid "That's what brought me to town."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "159||||4"
msgid "Can ya give us some details?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "160||||4"
msgid "Take a seat first, Aniki.\r\nY'can tell us all about the kid after."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "161||||4"
msgid "(I should check in with the family patriarch.\r\nWould be rude not to at least say hello.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "162||||4"
msgid "Is that our Tokyo man?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "163||||4"
msgid "Yeah. I was in the neighborhood."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "164||||4"
msgid "C'mon in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "165||||4"
msgid "Hm? And who's this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "166||||4"
msgid "Hey, Haruto!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "167||||4"
msgid "Don't worry 'bout it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "168||||4"
msgid "How've you been?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "169||||4"
msgid "My boys givin' ya any trouble?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "170||||4"
msgid "You've raised a good crew."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "171||||4"
msgid "Heh, right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "173||||4"
msgid "Nagumo told me about how you two met."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "174||||4"
msgid "Y'really saved his skin back there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "175||||4"
msgid "Though 'cause of that, things're iffy\r\nwith the Masuzoe Family now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "176||||4"
msgid "You know they're lookin' into you now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "177||||4"
msgid "Are they?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "178||||4"
msgid "I'm just a regular civilian, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "179||||4"
msgid "I'll try not to make any more\r\ntrouble for your family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "180||||4"
msgid "Nagumo invited you in to make up\r\nfor how he treated you before."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "181||||4"
msgid "I think he's ready to deal with\r\nwhatever consequences that brings."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "182||||4"
msgid "Y'like sitting on grandpa's lap, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "183||||4"
msgid "Sorry about him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "184||||4"
msgid "Here, go on back to yer pa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "185||||4"
msgid "Well, I should be going now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "186||||4"
msgid "Already? Come back soon then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "187||||4"
msgid "I've done nothing but sit around\r\nsince getting out of the hospital."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "188||||4"
msgid "Livin' off insurance is boring."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "189||||4"
msgid "I'll stop by some other time, then.\r\nGoodbye then, Patriarch."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "190||||4"
msgid "Aniki, y'leavin' already?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "191||||4"
msgid "I am. Thanks for having me over."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "192||||4"
msgid "Are y'gonna keep lookin'\r\nfer the kid's dad?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "193||||4"
msgid "You can forget about that now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "194||||4"
msgid "Huh? And, uh...\r\nWhy's that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "195||||4"
msgid "Don't worry.\r\nSee you later."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "197||||4"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-san!\r\nThere you are."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "198||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "199||||4"
msgid "Those Masuzoe Family guys from\r\nlast night were just over by my bar."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "200||||4"
msgid "They said they're looking\r\nfor you, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "201||||4"
msgid "You came all the way here\r\njust to tell me that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "202||||4"
msgid "Isn't it important enough?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "203||||4"
msgid "You don't want them picking fights\r\nwith you when Haruto's around."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "204||||4"
msgid "I guess that's true."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "205||||4"
msgid "If we just stand here though,\r\nthey'll find us in no time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "206||||4"
msgid "This way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "207||||4"
msgid "Let's take the back streets."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "208||||4"
msgid "We can head up to Ryunan Shrine,\r\na quiet little spot on the hill."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "209||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san. This way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "210||||4"
msgid "Hurry up, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "211||||4"
msgid "Hold on, Kiryu-san.\r\nWhere are you going?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "212||||4"
msgid "The Masuzoe Family is going to\r\nfind you if we don't hurry up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "213||||4"
msgid "Hey, would y'take a look at that?\r\nA guy n' his baby!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "214||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san! Be careful!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "216||||4"
msgid "Can I help you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "217||||4"
msgid "Don't go playin' dumb with us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "218||||4"
msgid "Did y'forget what y'did last night?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "219||||4"
msgid "We need t'borrow ya fer a bit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "220||||4"
msgid "But I guess we should probly\r\nrough ya up first."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "221||||4"
msgid "Don't go makin' this hard fer yerself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "222||||4"
msgid "Mama. Can you take Haruto for me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "223||||4"
msgid "Come on, Haruto-kun.\r\nOver here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "224||||4"
msgid "This guy ain't no ordinary grampa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "225||||4"
msgid "Don't hold anythin' back!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "226||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... Are you okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "227||||4"
msgid "Yeah.\r\nHaruto doing okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "228||||4"
msgid "Yeah, he's fine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "229||||4"
msgid "Thanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "230||||4"
msgid "We should keep moving before\r\nmore of them come."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "231||||4"
msgid "Ryunan Shrine.\r\nThis is it, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "232||||4"
msgid "Let's rest here for now.\r\nBut Kiryu-san, this is getting bad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "233||||4"
msgid "If the Masuzoe Family gets their hands\r\non you before you find Haruto's dad..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "234||||4"
msgid "I know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "235||||4"
msgid "Honestly, things haven't looked good\r\never since I met Nagumo in your bar."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "237||||4"
msgid "But I did figure something out\r\nfrom talking to the Hirose Family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "238||||4"
msgid "It's about Haruka.\r\nShe was definitely here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "239||||4"
msgid "Huh? What do you mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "240||||4"
msgid "(Those guys are probably at Moreno...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "241||||4"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-aniki..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "242||||4"
msgid "Um, thank you so much for saving me\r\nfrom those terrible thugs yesterday!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "243||||4"
msgid "I could really see myself falling\r\nfor a guy like you, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "244||||4"
msgid "R-Right. That's okay..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "245||||4"
msgid "Can't y'see he ain't interested?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "246||||4"
msgid "What's yer problem?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "247||||4"
msgid "If Matsunaga-aniki wants customers,\r\nhe oughta look for a hotter girl."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "248||||4"
msgid "Fer some reason,\r\nhe likes 'em butch."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "249||||4"
msgid "With our one hostess lookin' like that,\r\nthe place'll stay a ghost town."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "250||||4"
msgid "And where's Matsunaga now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "251||||4"
msgid "Jus' back there.\r\nGo ahead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "252||||4"
msgid "Yamato... The biggest\r\nbattleship ever built."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "253||||4"
msgid "It's a national treasure\r\nbuilt right here in Hiroshima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "254||||4"
msgid "Looks almost done."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "255||||4"
msgid "I didn't realize you were\r\ninterested in these."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "256||||4"
msgid "I was born in a shipbuildin' town. Every\r\nman, young or old, loves all sorts o' ships."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "257||||4"
msgid "I'm sorry for all the trouble\r\nI caused in here last night, Matsunaga."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "258||||4"
msgid "Y'were just tryin' to help, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "259||||4"
msgid "There's nothing to apologize about.\r\nDon't even sweat it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "260||||4"
msgid "But remember, I ain't your friend.\r\nNot yet."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "262||||4"
msgid "I guess I'm a harder nut to\r\ncrack than Captain Nagumo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "263||||4"
msgid "Heh, noted."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "264||||4"
msgid "Matsunaga-aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "265||||4"
msgid "Huh? What's up, Yuta?\r\nSomethin' happen?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "266||||4"
msgid "Y'know those customers from last night?\r\nThe shipbuilders?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "267||||4"
msgid "Yeah. What about 'em?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "268||||4"
msgid "Apparently they hightailed it to the Yomei\r\nAlliance to tattle on us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "269||||4"
msgid "The main family captain's over\r\nat our office now to settle things."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "270||||4"
msgid "Wait, their captain?\r\nShit, that's Koshimizu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "271||||4"
msgid "He's not alone. Masuzoe's along too,\r\nfresh off his bruises from the cap."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "272||||4"
msgid "I'd say they're like, 20 guys deep."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "273||||4"
msgid "Twenty guys? All at our place?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "275||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "276||||4"
msgid "Captain Nagumo said t'come\r\nget you, Matsunaga-aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "277||||4"
msgid "I see."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "278||||4"
msgid "I'm probly gonna have t'chop off\r\na pinky over this nonsense."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "279||||4"
msgid "But why you, Matsunaga-aniki?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "280||||4"
msgid "Y'weren't the one beatin'\r\non the customers last night."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "282||||4"
msgid "Don't be dumb.\r\nIt's a Hirose bar, and I run it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "283||||4"
msgid "I've gotta take responsibility,\r\neven fer a fight between customers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "284||||4"
msgid "I can't pin it all on Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "285||||4"
msgid "But y'know... Kiryu-san ain't\r\nfrom around here, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "286||||4"
msgid "If we get him to apologize to 'em..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "287||||4"
msgid "Y'think I'm gonna do somethin'\r\nthat pathetic? Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "288||||4"
msgid "I know we're chumps for yakuza n' all,\r\nbut I ain't gonna sell Hirose short."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "289||||4"
msgid "Hold on. I have a question first."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "290||||4"
msgid "How is a drunken brawl enough to bring their\r\ncaptain to a small family office like yours?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "291||||4"
msgid "An outsider would never understand."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "292||||4"
msgid "This town's the home base\r\nfor Iwami Shipbuilding."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "293||||4"
msgid "Iwami Shipbuilding?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "294||||4"
msgid "It's where some o' the drunks\r\nfrom last night work."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "295||||4"
msgid "Iwami's one o' the biggest shipbuildin'\r\nbusinesses the world over."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "296||||4"
msgid "They got tonsa influence, 'specially\r\n'round here. Schools, hospitals, y'name it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "297||||4"
msgid "Everyone in Hiroshima's connected\r\nto Iwami one way or another."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "298||||4"
msgid "Anybody who dares to rise up at 'em,\r\nyer life in Hiroshima may as well be over."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "299||||4"
msgid "And even the Yomei Alliance bows to them?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "300||||4"
msgid "That's enough talk.\r\nThis don't concern ya, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "301||||4"
msgid "Jus' act like y'never heard\r\nany o' this. Now then..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "302||||4"
msgid "Matsunaga, don't pretend like you can\r\nhandle this alone. I'm going with you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "303||||4"
msgid "Yuta. Tagashira.\r\nDon't let Kiryu-san leave this bar."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "304||||4"
msgid "What? But..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "305||||4"
msgid "That's an order from yer aniki.\r\nDon't make me repeat m'self."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "306||||4"
msgid "These're Matsunaga-aniki's orders, Kiryu-san.\r\nJus' stay here and cool off fer a bit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "308||||4"
msgid "Please. You need to stop sticking\r\nyer nose where it doesn't belong."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "309||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "310||||4"
msgid "Looks like we really can't\r\ncall you our aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "311||||4"
msgid "We're not quite like Captain Nagumo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "312||||4"
msgid "I understand the point you're trying\r\nto prove, but you need to step aside."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "313||||4"
msgid "Are y'trying to shame Matsunaga-aniki?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "314||||4"
msgid "I started the fight last night."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "315||||4"
msgid "If anything, you're the ones\r\nwho should be staying out of this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "316||||4"
msgid "All you two did was sit around and\r\nget your punk asses beaten."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "317||||4"
msgid "What was that!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "318||||4"
msgid "Damn you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "319||||4"
msgid "Move."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "320||||4"
msgid "If I don't hurry, Matsunaga's done!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "321||||4"
msgid "You think you scare us!?\r\nBring it, old man!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "322||||4"
msgid "Don't take this personally."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "323||||4"
msgid "W-Wait! Please, stop!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "325||||4"
msgid "You're all alone. How do ya\r\nthink you're gonna settle this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "326||||4"
msgid "You gonna offer up your pinky\r\nin Matsunaga-aniki's place?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "327||||4"
msgid "I just want to talk to these Yomei guys.\r\nHow they respond is up to them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "328||||4"
msgid "Y'don't understand. They control\r\nevery last yakuza in Hiroshima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "329||||4"
msgid "Y'can't just go in swinging!\r\nDo you hear a word I'm saying!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "331||||4"
msgid "Sides, we jus' met ya!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "332||||4"
msgid "And yer still tryin' to risk\r\nyer life to save Matsunaga-aniki?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "333||||4"
msgid "Why're y'doin' this!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "334||||4"
msgid "You guys knew Haruka.\r\nAnd I know you're hiding it from me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "335||||4"
msgid "Wh-Where's this comin' from...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "336||||4"
msgid "The more I help you, the more willing\r\nyou'll be to tell me what I want."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "337||||4"
msgid "I've got my own motives for doing this.\r\nAnd charity isn't one of them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "339||||4"
msgid "Yeah, right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "340||||4"
msgid "If info's all you wanted, you could've\r\njust beat on us 'til we talked."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "341||||4"
msgid "Interesting. I never thought of that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "342||||4"
msgid "Wh-What's that s'posed t'mean...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "343||||4"
msgid "Seriously... What's the deal with him?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "344||||4"
msgid "(Matsunaga should be at the Hirose office.\r\nI need to get there, and fast...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "345||||4"
msgid "Y'finally showed up.\r\nBeen lookin' fer ya... Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "346||||4"
msgid "Masuzoe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "347||||4"
msgid "I owe ya one fer last night."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "348||||4"
msgid "But first, who in the hell are ya?\r\nWhat brought ya crawlin' into town?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "349||||4"
msgid "My business here isn't with you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "350||||4"
msgid "I heard there's a Yomei captain here.\r\nHe's the one I want, so get out of my way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "351||||4"
msgid "Guess y'really don't understand\r\nwhat's goin' on here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "352||||4"
msgid "Yer 'bout to become history."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "353||||4"
msgid "What y'do now determines\r\nwhether or not I let ya live."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "354||||4"
msgid "That's funny.\r\nI was thinking the same thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "355||||4"
msgid "Step aside if you don't want to die.\r\nIf you leave now, I'll let this slide."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "356||||4"
msgid "I'm sick o' yer smug bullshit. But that's gonna\r\nmake it even more satisfyin' to beat yer ass."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "357||||4"
msgid "Time's up.\r\nLet's go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "358||||4"
msgid "Wait, the Tojo Clan Fourth Chairman?\r\nY'mean like, the Tojo Clan from Tokyo!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "359||||4"
msgid "That one."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "361||||4"
msgid "Then... I know who y'are. The Dragon o' Dojima!\r\nI read about ya in a magazine once."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "362||||4"
msgid "Hey, what's up with y'guys?\r\nWhy aren't ya surprised?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "363||||4"
msgid "Is he really that famous?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "364||||4"
msgid "Huh? What're y'talkin' about!?\r\nHe's legendary fer bein' a ruthless yakuza!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "365||||4"
msgid "This guy's incredible!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "366||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-aniki. Why'd y'try to hide this\r\nfrom us? Y'should've told us way sooner."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "367||||4"
msgid "I left that life in the past.\r\nI'm just a civilian now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "368||||4"
msgid "But I guess there's nothing left to hide."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "369||||4"
msgid "At least, <font_kind=yakuza_italic>I'm</font_kind> not hiding anything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "370||||4"
msgid "What d'ya mean, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "371||||4"
msgid "He means there's still\r\nsomethin' we're hiding from him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "372||||4"
msgid "That's what he means."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "373||||4"
msgid "Oh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "374||||4"
msgid "Well, what're ya hiding?\r\nC'mon, Nagumo. I can keep a secret."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "375||||4"
msgid "Huh? W-Well, uh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "377||||4"
msgid "It's fine. I'm heading home for tonight.\r\nI need to get back to Haruto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "378||||4"
msgid "Hey, Nagumo.\r\nLet's hear this secret."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "379||||4"
msgid "(Mama said she'd bring Haruto back to the\r\napartment. She's probably waiting there.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "380||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "381||||4"
msgid "Hi there. Sorry I'm late.\r\nHave you been here long?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "382||||4"
msgid "Not really. Haruto-kun's fast asleep.\r\nHe's been in a great mood today, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "383||||4"
msgid "That's good. Did you want to\r\ncome inside for a bit?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "384||||4"
msgid "Oh no, it's getting late. Anyway,\r\nhow are things with the Masuzoe Family?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "385||||4"
msgid "Fine, for now at least."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "386||||4"
msgid "I'm glad to hear that.\r\nWell, here's Haruto-kun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "387||||4"
msgid "I really shouldn't keep asking you\r\nto take care of him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "388||||4"
msgid "What about the Hirose guys?\r\nDid they tell you anything about Haruka?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "389||||4"
msgid "No, I didn't get the chance to ask."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "390||||4"
msgid "I'll give it some more time.\r\nI still think they'll come clean themselves."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "392||||4"
msgid "Is something wrong?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "393||||4"
msgid "No no, it's nothing.\r\nWell, good night."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "394||||4"
msgid "Same to you. Thanks again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "396||||4"
msgid "Aniki. It's Nagumo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "397||||4"
msgid "Nagumo...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "398||||4"
msgid "Kiyo-chan told me where yer stayin'.\r\nI've got somethin' I wanna tell ya, Aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "399||||4"
msgid "Haruto's sleeping, so let's talk outside.\r\nDo you mind?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "400||||4"
msgid "Not a lick."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "401||||4"
msgid "As y'can probly guess,\r\nI came t'talk about Haruka-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "403||||4"
msgid "Truth is, everyone in the family\r\nknew Haruka-san when she was here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "404||||4"
msgid "Soon as y'showed us that picture over at\r\nthe office, we figured out who y'were."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "405||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-aniki. Yer Haruka's guardian and the\r\nTojo Clan Fourth Chairman... Kazuma Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "407||||4"
msgid "Pretty sure Matsunaga didn't quite\r\nput the pieces together, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "408||||4"
msgid "Lemme tell ya, that thick skull o' his\r\nserves him good sometimes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "409||||4"
msgid "I see."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "410||||4"
msgid "Sorry fer how rude we were to ya.\r\nHope ya can accept my apology."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "411||||4"
msgid "Oh, and there's a reason we didn't tell\r\nya 'bout us knowin' Haruka-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "412||||4"
msgid "She never gave us permission."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "413||||4"
msgid "Go on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "414||||4"
msgid "Haruka-san blew in to town\r\nsomewhere 'round three years ago."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "415||||4"
msgid "At first, she didn't much feel like\r\ntalkin' about herself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "416||||4"
msgid "She was always careful\r\no' who could've been around."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "417||||4"
msgid "T'be honest, it looked kinda like\r\nshe'd ran away from home t'come here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "419||||4"
msgid "Here in the sticks,\r\noutsiders stand out like a sore thumb."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "420||||4"
msgid "But she was the cutest girl yokels like\r\nus'd ever seen. She got popular real quick."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "421||||4"
msgid "Whenever Haruka-san was 'round..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "422||||4"
msgid "...Everyone'd be on their best behavior.\r\nMy family, the shipbuilders, the fishermen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "423||||4"
msgid "Soon enough, people took t'thinkin' of her\r\nas a damn important part of Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "424||||4"
msgid "Nobody could bring 'emselves to\r\nmention her past life as a celebrity."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "425||||4"
msgid "So you did know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "426||||4"
msgid "Don't even need to watch TV to\r\nsort that out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "427||||4"
msgid "We knew Haruka-san was tryin'\r\nt'stay outta the public eye, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "429||||4"
msgid "We jus' wanted t'protect her from\r\nthe world she was hopin' to escape."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "430||||4"
msgid "That's why we were tryin' to hide\r\nwhat we knew about her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "431||||4"
msgid "I know y'wanted info\r\non Haruka-san, Aniki..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "432||||4"
msgid "...But we jus' couldn't do that t'her.\r\nThe whole town probly thought the same."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "433||||4"
msgid "Huh, you're more considerate than I took\r\nyou for. I can see why Haruka felt at home."
msgstr ""

